commit.message:
Fix PAT hover: use customdata for company name, not invalid %{fullData.name}

%{fullData.name} is not valid Plotly template syntax and fails silently.
Pass name via custom_data=['name'] in px.line and use %{customdata[0]}
in the template — guaranteed to resolve to the company name string.

